<h2 class=\"firstheader\">synopsis:</h2>
<p>
The Current Sessions: Vol I, Issue I, is a live art/performance showcase devised to create works that are solely in-the-moment and in one\'s current state of mind and creative process. The evening includes works and works-in-progress by emerging choreographers Alexis Convento, Allison Jones, Yarden Raz, Jonathan Royse Windham, and Yin Yue.</p>
<p>Our mission is to bring to an audience new choreographic works which show original creative flow, risk-taking to challenge one’s mind, and the overall openness to achieve a higher ground in the development of dance and art itself.</p>
